data.description:
A freshly painted interior, fully fenced backyard, a gorgeous sunroom, a long driveway, and over 3,200 sq ft of living space are among the many things offered by this beautiful 5 bedroom 3.5 bath home sitting on a third of an acre on a quiet cul-de-sac in the highly coveted Patriots Ridge Subdivision!!! 

The main living area, as you enter the home, is open with hardwood floors in the dining room, kitchen, and breakfast area while there is carpet in the great room. The kitchen has a pantry, stained cabinets, granite counters, including a breakfast bar, and natural stone tile back splash. Stainless steel appliances, refrigerator remains. The large owners bedroom, on the main floor, has a beautiful trey ceiling. The large owner's bath has a double granite vanity, a garden tub, and a separate shower. 


The remaining 4 bedrooms are upstairs. Two share a Jack n Jill bathroom with an additional hall bathroom. The 5th bedroom/bonus room has a large closet. There is a sun room with doors coming from the breakfast area and the great room. 

This home has so much to offer. It is within walking distance from the community pool and it is also just up the street from Patriots Park and the Columbia County Fairgrounds. Close to I-20, Fort Eisenhower, shopping, and restaurants.

Schedule your private showings today!
